                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Katie tattoo
                              Katie Holmes and Tom Cruise in Sevilla, Spain. (AP)                            
	London, Dec. 29 (PTI): Actress Katie Holmes is reportedly desperate to get a tattoo inked to show her love for superstar-husband Tom Cruise.         
	The Batman Begins star, who has been married to Cruise for four years now, wants a tattoo to prove her devotion to him but the 47-year-old actor is trying to convince her otherwise, reports www.Contactmusic.com reported.         
	Hes desperately trying to talk her out of getting the tattoo, said a source. The 31-year-old actress came up with the idea after seeing the etching friend and former Spice Girl Victoria Beckham had got to mark her 10-year wedding anniversary earlier this year.        
	Beckham had the Hebrew words for Together, Forever, Eternally inked on her wrist in honour of her soccer star husband David and Holmes is determined to get a similar inscription.                                                                                                                                                          
